575
00:39:17.480 --> 00:39:20.450
King Viserys of House Targaryen.

576
00:39:20.520 --> 00:39:22.510
the First of His Name.

577
00:39:22.620 --> 00:39:27.030
King of the Andals and the Rhoynar

578
00:39:22.620 --> 00:39:27.030
and the First Men.

579
00:39:28.060 --> 00:39:31.960
Lord of the Seven Kingdoms

580
00:39:28.060 --> 00:39:31.960
and Protector of the Realm.

581
00:40:52.480 --> 00:40:54.410
I will sit the throne today.

582
00:40:56.280 --> 00:40:57.310
Your Grace.

583
00:41:04.920 --> 00:41:07.330
I will be fine. I will be fine.

584
00:41:21.570 --> 00:41:22.970
I said I'm fine.

585
00:41:26.810 --> 00:41:27.800
Come on.

586
00:41:35.290 --> 00:41:36.690
Steady.

587
00:42:18.160 --> 00:42:23.030
I must... admit... my confusion.

588
00:42:25.240 --> 00:42:27.500
I do not understand

589
00:42:27.570 --> 00:42:31.980
why petitions are being heard

590
00:42:27.570 --> 00:42:31.980
over a settled succession.

591
00:42:32.050 --> 00:42:33.210
The only one present...

592
00:42:34.350 --> 00:42:38.980
who might offer keener insight

593
00:42:34.350 --> 00:42:38.980
into Lord Corlys's wishes

594
00:42:39.050 --> 00:42:40.850
is the Princess Rhaenys.

595
00:42:44.590 --> 00:42:45.580
Indeed. Your Grace.

596
00:43:00.170 --> 00:43:03.270
It was ever my husband's

597
00:43:00.170 --> 00:43:03.270
will that Driftmark

598
00:43:03.380 --> 00:43:06.040
pass through Ser Laenor

599
00:43:06.110 --> 00:43:07.710
to his trueborn son...

600
00:43:08.750 --> 00:43:10.880
Lucerys Velaryon.

601
00:43:10.950 --> 00:43:12.680
His mind never changed.

602
00:43:13.750 --> 00:43:15.950
Nor did my support of him.

603
00:43:16.960 --> 00:43:18.620
As a matter of fact.

604
00:43:16.960 --> 00:43:18.620
the Princess Rhaenyra

605
00:43:18.720 --> 00:43:20.220
has just informed me of her desire

606
00:43:20.290 --> 00:43:21.960
to marry her sons Jace and Luke

607
00:43:22.060 --> 00:43:24.900
to Lord Corlys's granddaughters.

608
00:43:22.060 --> 00:43:24.900
Baela and Rhaena.

609
00:43:26.300 --> 00:43:29.930
A proposal to which I heartily agree.

610
00:43:31.400 --> 00:43:34.810
Well...

611
00:43:31.400 --> 00:43:34.810
the matter is settled.

612
00:43:36.280 --> 00:43:37.640
Again.

613
00:43:38.780 --> 00:43:44.080
I hereby reaffirm

614
00:43:38.780 --> 00:43:44.080
Prince Lucerys of House Velaryon

615
00:43:44.150 --> 00:43:46.310
as heir to Driftmark.

616
00:43:46.420 --> 00:43:50.410
the Driftwood Throne.

617
00:43:46.420 --> 00:43:50.410
and the next Lord of the Tides.

618
00:43:57.760 --> 00:43:59.390
You break law...

619
00:44:00.570 --> 00:44:02.300
and centuries of tradition

620
00:44:03.270 --> 00:44:05.470
to install your daughter as heir.

621
00:44:06.510 --> 00:44:08.270
Yet you dare tell me...

622
00:44:09.340 --> 00:44:11.900
who deserves

623
00:44:09.340 --> 00:44:11.900
to inherit the name Velaryon.

624
00:44:14.580 --> 00:44:15.570
No.

625
00:44:16.920 --> 00:44:19.010
I will not allow it.

626
00:44:19.990 --> 00:44:21.080
"Allow it"?

627
00:44:22.520 --> 00:44:24.750
Do not forget yourself. Vaemond.

628
00:44:28.790 --> 00:44:33.360
That is no true Velaryon.

629
00:44:33.470 --> 00:44:36.660
and certainly no nephew of mine.

630
00:44:36.770 --> 00:44:38.830
Go to your chambers.

631
00:44:36.770 --> 00:44:38.830
You have said enough.

632
00:44:40.270 --> 00:44:43.680
Lucerys is my true-born grandson.

633
00:44:44.710 --> 00:44:46.270
And you...

634
00:44:46.350 --> 00:44:49.840
are no more

635
00:44:46.350 --> 00:44:49.840
than the second son of Driftmark.

636
00:44:50.950 --> 00:44:55.550
You... may run your house

637
00:44:50.950 --> 00:44:55.550
as you see fit...

638
00:44:56.660 --> 00:44:59.460
but you will not decide

639
00:44:56.660 --> 00:44:59.460
the future of mine.

640
00:45:01.530 --> 00:45:03.550
My house survived the Doom

641
00:45:03.660 --> 00:45:06.830
and a thousand tribulations besides.

642
00:45:06.900 --> 00:45:08.660
And gods be damned...

643
00:45:09.900 --> 00:45:15.640
I will not see it ended

644
00:45:09.900 --> 00:45:15.640
on the account of this--

645
00:45:17.340 --> 00:45:18.330
Say it.

646
00:45:29.320 --> 00:45:30.420
Her children...

647
00:45:31.560 --> 00:45:33.420
are bastards!

648
00:45:37.160 --> 00:45:38.430
And she...

649
00:45:39.330 --> 00:45:40.360
is...

650
00:45:41.170 --> 00:45:42.230
a whore.

651
00:45:49.110 --> 00:45:50.170
I...

652
00:45:52.040 --> 00:45:53.440
will have your tongue for that.

653
00:46:01.020 --> 00:46:02.390
He can keep his tongue.

654
00:46:03.620 --> 00:46:05.110
- Disarm him!

655
00:46:03.620 --> 00:46:05.110
- No need.

656
00:46:13.770 --> 00:46:15.740
Call the maesters!

657
00:46:13.770 --> 00:46:15.740
- Father?

658
00:46:15.800 --> 00:46:18.270
Please. my love.

659
00:46:15.800 --> 00:46:18.270
You must take something for the pain.

660
00:46:19.740 --> 00:46:21.230
I will not cloud my mind.

661
00:46:22.410 --> 00:46:24.640
I must put things right.

662
00:47:09.820 --> 00:47:13.850
The body will be ready for its return

663
00:47:09.820 --> 00:47:13.850
to Driftmark on the morrow. my lady.

664
00:47:17.130 --> 00:47:20.120
You may wish to leave the Silent Sisters

665
00:47:17.130 --> 00:47:20.120
to their work.

666
00:47:21.200 --> 00:47:23.860
It is ill luck to look

667
00:47:21.200 --> 00:47:23.860
upon the face of death.

668
00:47:28.210 --> 00:47:32.110
The Stranger has visited me more times

669
00:47:28.210 --> 00:47:32.110
than I can count. Grand Maester.

670
00:47:37.150 --> 00:47:38.280
I assure you...

671
00:47:39.690 --> 00:47:43.120
he cares little whether my eyes

672
00:47:39.690 --> 00:47:43.120
are open or closed.

673
00:49:09.070 --> 00:49:12.640
How good it is

674
00:49:09.070 --> 00:49:12.640
to see you all tonight...

675
00:49:13.780 --> 00:49:15.080
together.

676
00:49:20.890 --> 00:49:22.910
- Prayer before we begin?

677
00:49:20.890 --> 00:49:22.910
- Yes.

678
00:49:24.920 --> 00:49:27.220
May the Mother smile down

679
00:49:24.920 --> 00:49:27.220
on this gathering with love.

680
00:49:28.160 --> 00:49:31.890
May the Smith mend the bonds

681
00:49:28.160 --> 00:49:31.890
that have been broken for far too long.

682
00:49:31.960 --> 00:49:35.160
And to Vaemond Velaryon.

683
00:49:31.960 --> 00:49:35.160
may the gods give him rest.

684
00:49:43.240 --> 00:49:46.080
This is an occasion for celebration.

685
00:49:43.240 --> 00:49:46.080
it seems.

686
00:49:47.110 --> 00:49:49.670
My grandsons. Jace and Luke.

687
00:49:49.780 --> 00:49:52.950
will marry their cousins.

688
00:49:49.780 --> 00:49:52.950
Baela and Rhaena.

689
00:49:53.020 --> 00:49:55.780
further strengthening the bond

690
00:49:53.020 --> 00:49:55.780
between our houses.

691
00:49:56.460 --> 00:49:58.920
A toast to the young princes...

692
00:49:59.860 --> 00:50:02.260
- and their betrothed.

693
00:49:59.860 --> 00:50:02.260
- Hear. hear!

694
00:50:03.330 --> 00:50:05.920
Well done. Jace.

695
00:50:03.330 --> 00:50:05.920
You'll finally get to lie with a woman.

696
00:50:06.930 --> 00:50:09.960
Let us toast as well Prince Lucerys...

697
00:50:11.470 --> 00:50:14.130
the future Lord of the Tides.

698
00:50:14.210 --> 00:50:15.700
Hear. hear.

699
00:50:15.810 --> 00:50:16.780
You'll be great.

700
00:50:20.880 --> 00:50:24.320
You do know

701
00:50:20.880 --> 00:50:24.320
how the act is done. I assume?

702
00:50:25.280 --> 00:50:26.380
At least in principle?

703
00:50:26.490 --> 00:50:27.890
Where to put your cock and all that.

704
00:50:27.990 --> 00:50:29.350
Let it be. cousin.

705
00:50:29.460 --> 00:50:31.120
You can play the jester if you wish.

706
00:50:31.190 --> 00:50:33.220
but hold your tongue

707
00:50:31.190 --> 00:50:33.220
before my betrothed.

708
00:50:33.330 --> 00:50:34.220
Hmm.

709
00:50:54.750 --> 00:50:57.880
It both gladdens my heart

710
00:50:59.250 --> 00:51:01.880
and fills me with sorrow

711
00:51:03.560 --> 00:51:06.580
to see these faces around the table.

712
00:51:08.030 --> 00:51:11.230
The faces most dear

713
00:51:08.030 --> 00:51:11.230
to me in all the world...

714
00:51:13.200 --> 00:51:15.330
yet grown so distant from each other...

715
00:51:16.400 --> 00:51:17.700
in the years past.

716
00:51:42.360 --> 00:51:43.690
My own face...

717
00:51:45.060 --> 00:51:47.260
is no longer a handsome one...

718
00:51:49.970 --> 00:51:51.600
if indeed it ever was.

719
00:51:55.210 --> 00:51:56.300
But tonight...

720
00:51:57.310 --> 00:52:00.400
I wish you to see me as I am.

721
00:52:01.950 --> 00:52:03.580
Not just a king...

722
00:52:05.250 --> 00:52:06.450
but your father.

723
00:52:08.220 --> 00:52:09.280
Your brother.

724
00:52:10.160 --> 00:52:11.280
Your husband...

725
00:52:14.260 --> 00:52:15.590
and your grandsire.

726
00:52:16.930 --> 00:52:18.400
Who may not. it seems...

727
00:52:19.930 --> 00:52:21.730
walk for much longer among you.

728
00:52:27.810 --> 00:52:29.740
Let us no longer hold

729
00:52:29.810 --> 00:52:31.740
- ill feelings in our hearts.

730
00:52:33.480 --> 00:52:35.180
The Crown cannot stand strong

731
00:52:35.280 --> 00:52:37.650
if the House of the Dragon

732
00:52:35.280 --> 00:52:37.650
remains divided.

733
00:52:38.920 --> 00:52:40.820
- But set aside your grievances.

734
00:52:45.090 --> 00:52:47.290
If not for the sake of the Crown...

735
00:52:48.190 --> 00:52:50.130
then for the sake of this old man

736
00:52:51.530 --> 00:52:52.760
who loves you all

737
00:52:54.200 --> 00:52:55.260
so dearly.

738
00:53:22.560 --> 00:53:25.550
I wish to raise my cup

739
00:53:22.560 --> 00:53:25.550
to Her Grace. the Queen.

740
00:53:29.840 --> 00:53:31.000
I love my father.

741
00:53:32.200 --> 00:53:34.640
But I must admit

742
00:53:32.200 --> 00:53:34.640
that no one has stood...

743
00:53:35.710 --> 00:53:37.900
more loyally by his side

744
00:53:35.710 --> 00:53:37.900
than his good wife.

745
00:53:41.410 --> 00:53:43.210
She has tended to him with...

746
00:53:44.550 --> 00:53:46.520
unfailing devotion.

747
00:53:46.590 --> 00:53:49.210
love. and honor.

748
00:53:50.390 --> 00:53:53.220
And for that. she has my gratitude...

749
00:53:55.030 --> 00:53:56.090
and my apology.

750
00:54:06.000 --> 00:54:08.840
Your graciousness

751
00:54:06.000 --> 00:54:08.840
moves me deeply. Princess.

752
00:54:11.910 --> 00:54:13.240
We are both mothers

753
00:54:16.380 --> 00:54:17.580
and we love our children.

754
00:54:21.690 --> 00:54:24.350
We have more in common

755
00:54:21.690 --> 00:54:24.350
than we sometimes allow.

756
00:54:27.530 --> 00:54:30.860
I raise my cup to you and to your house.

757
00:54:36.440 --> 00:54:37.730
You will make a fine queen.

758
00:55:14.310 --> 00:55:15.500
I. um...

759
00:55:16.580 --> 00:55:18.840
I regret the disappointment

760
00:55:16.580 --> 00:55:18.840
you are soon to suffer.

761
00:55:20.010 --> 00:55:23.450
But if you ever wish to know

762
00:55:20.010 --> 00:55:23.450
what it is to be well satisfied.

763
00:55:23.520 --> 00:55:25.680
- all you have to do is ask.

764
00:55:26.150 --> 00:55:27.140
Jace.

765
00:55:56.010 --> 00:56:00.110
To Prince Aegon and Prince Aemond.

766
00:56:00.190 --> 00:56:03.490
We have not seen each other in years.

767
00:56:03.560 --> 00:56:06.390
but I have fond memories

768
00:56:03.560 --> 00:56:06.390
of our shared youth.

769
00:56:08.730 --> 00:56:12.360
And as men. I hope we may

770
00:56:08.730 --> 00:56:12.360
yet be friends and allies.

771
00:56:13.830 --> 00:56:16.460
To you and your family's

772
00:56:13.830 --> 00:56:16.460
good health. dear uncles.

773
00:56:24.340 --> 00:56:25.330
To you as well.

774
00:56:33.250 --> 00:56:35.650
Beware the beast beneath the boards.

775
00:56:35.720 --> 00:56:37.160
Well done. my boys.

776
00:56:37.220 --> 00:56:39.690
I would like to toast

777
00:56:37.220 --> 00:56:39.690
to Baela and Rhaena.

778
00:56:40.730 --> 00:56:42.060
They'll be married soon.

779
00:56:43.860 --> 00:56:46.420
It isn't so bad.

780
00:56:43.860 --> 00:56:46.420
Mostly he just ignores you...

781
00:56:48.200 --> 00:56:50.100
except sometimes when he's drunk.

782
00:56:58.540 --> 00:57:01.210
- Good.

783
00:56:58.540 --> 00:57:01.210
- Let us have some music.

784
00:57:07.190 --> 00:57:08.410
Excuse me.

785
00:58:40.280 --> 00:58:41.800
Guards.

786
00:58:49.960 --> 00:58:51.320
Please. sit down.

787
00:59:31.030 --> 00:59:32.090
Final tribute.

788
00:59:35.370 --> 00:59:36.860
To the health of my nephews.

789
00:59:38.240 --> 00:59:39.100
Jace...

790
00:59:40.870 --> 00:59:41.770
Luke...

791
00:59:43.180 --> 00:59:44.270
and Joffrey.

792
00:59:45.610 --> 00:59:48.580
Each of them handsome. wise...

793
00:59:56.290 --> 00:59:57.780
- strong.

794
00:59:56.290 --> 00:59:57.780
- Aemond.

795
00:59:57.890 --> 00:59:58.880
Come...

796
01:00:00.760 --> 01:00:03.960
let us drain our cups to these three...

797
01:00:05.060 --> 01:00:07.290
- Strong boys.

798
01:00:05.060 --> 01:00:07.290
- I dare you to say that again.

799
01:00:07.400 --> 01:00:09.800
Why? 'Twas only a compliment.

800
01:00:10.470 --> 01:00:12.400
- Do you not think yourself Strong?

801
01:00:12.540 --> 01:00:14.770
Jace!

802
01:00:12.540 --> 01:00:14.770
That is enough!

803
01:00:21.550 --> 01:00:23.710
Why would you say such a thing

804
01:00:21.550 --> 01:00:23.710
before these people?

805
01:00:23.780 --> 01:00:26.980
I was merely expressing how proud I am

806
01:00:23.780 --> 01:00:26.980
of my family. Mother.

807
01:00:27.090 --> 01:00:30.720
Mmm. Though it seems my nephews

808
01:00:27.090 --> 01:00:30.720
aren't quite as proud of theirs.

809
01:00:30.790 --> 01:00:31.950
Wait. wait!

810
01:00:36.290 --> 01:00:38.790
Go to your quarters.

811
01:00:36.290 --> 01:00:38.790
All of you go. now.

812
01:00:50.510 --> 01:00:51.340
Hmm.

813
01:00:58.820 --> 01:00:59.810
Rhaenyra.

814
01:01:03.790 --> 01:01:06.520
It's best. I think.

815
01:01:03.790 --> 01:01:06.520
if we go back to Dragonstone.

816
01:01:06.630 --> 01:01:08.120
You've only just arrived.

817
01:01:14.600 --> 01:01:15.830
Let me see the children home.

818
01:01:17.470 --> 01:01:18.770
I'll. um...

819
01:01:19.870 --> 01:01:21.170
return on dragonback.

820
01:01:26.280 --> 01:01:28.470
The King and I would both like that.

821
01:02:09.850 --> 01:02:13.190
It's been quite a night

822
01:02:09.850 --> 01:02:13.190
at the castle. it seems.

823
01:02:14.430 --> 01:02:15.490
Yes. my lady.

824
01:02:50.900 --> 01:02:52.120
Come on. come on.

825
01:02:56.230 --> 01:02:57.220
- That's it.

826
01:03:07.650 --> 01:03:08.480
Oh...

827
01:03:10.220 --> 01:03:11.410
Well done.

828
01:03:18.260 --> 01:03:20.730
- I'm sorry.

829
01:03:20.790 --> 01:03:22.060
I'm sorry.

830
01:03:25.160 --> 01:03:26.720
But you wanted to know...

831
01:03:28.070 --> 01:03:30.260
if I believe it to be true.

832
01:03:32.100 --> 01:03:33.730
Believe what to be true. my king?

833
01:03:34.810 --> 01:03:36.170
Don't you remember?

834
01:03:38.480 --> 01:03:39.670
Aegon...

835
01:03:42.350 --> 01:03:43.340
Our son?

836
01:03:45.750 --> 01:03:46.810
His dream.

837
01:03:47.820 --> 01:03:51.150
The Song of Ice... and Fi--

838
01:03:52.590 --> 01:03:53.580
It is true.

839
01:03:54.990 --> 01:03:56.590
What he saw in the North.

840
01:03:59.530 --> 01:04:01.260
The Prince That Was Promised.

841
01:04:02.670 --> 01:04:04.100
I don't understand. Viserys.

842
01:04:05.600 --> 01:04:07.130
The Prince.

843
01:04:07.210 --> 01:04:08.370
Prince Aegon?

844
01:04:10.040 --> 01:04:11.840
To unite the realm

845
01:04:11.940 --> 01:04:14.710
against the cold... and the dark.

846
01:04:18.620 --> 01:04:19.710
It is you.

847
01:04:23.120 --> 01:04:24.380
You are the one.

848
01:04:26.560 --> 01:04:28.030
You must do this.

849
01:04:30.130 --> 01:04:31.790
You must do this.

850
01:05:17.040 --> 01:05:18.170
I understand. my king.

851
01:05:39.400 --> 01:05:40.700
No more.

852
01:05:41.400 --> 01:05:42.390
No more.

853
01:06:11.760 --> 01:06:12.820
My love.
